title: Number of Burger King restaurants in the Asia Pacific region from 2012 to 2013
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 12 different Countrys for 2 groups 2012, and 2013 that are presented on the X-axis.
Country Australia had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for 2013. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Country Philippines for 2012.
In Country Australia, 2013 had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Country Thailand out of all 12 Countrys.
Country Australia and Thailand had the biggest gap of 337.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2013.
